{"title":"react脚手架搭建项目","slug":"react","date":"2020-02-12T12:00:23.000Z","updated":"2020-02-12T12:00:23.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/react.json","photos":[],"link":"","excerpt":"react脚手架搭建环境 [Figure] 3.灵活：React可以与已知的库或框架很好地配合。","covers":["https://i.loli.net/2020/02/12/A3jBvZuO5X2xdQa.gif","https://i.loli.net/2020/02/12/3Sh2PJ9XN16qKOg.png","https://i.loli.net/2020/02/12/tvIqEr4Su7Hs8OK.png","https://i.loli.net/2020/02/12/jFoBXCT9ixAQakE.png","https://i.loli.net/2020/02/12/UKp4xzgl7ivJ38T.png","https://i.loli.net/2020/02/12/toT4yDPMk9jRK2d.png","https://i.loli.net/2020/02/12/PZfhi3wXKCHSNJM.png"],"content":"<h3 id=\"react脚手架搭建环境\"><a href=\"#react脚手架搭建环境\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"react脚手架搭建环境\"></a>react脚手架搭建环境</h3><p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2020/02/12/A3jBvZuO5X2xdQa.gif\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p>特点：<br>1.声明式设计：React采用声明范式，可以轻松描述应用。<br>2.高效：React通过对DOM的模拟，最大限度地减少与DOM的交互。<br>3.灵活：React可以与已知的库或框架很好地配合。</p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n\n<p><strong>1.下载react脚手架</strong></p>\n<p>脚手架有多种，这是官方的：</p>\n<p>cmd 在终端执行</p>\n<p><code>npm install -g create-react-app</code></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2020/02/12/3Sh2PJ9XN16qKOg.png\" alt=\"react.PNG\"></p>\n<p><strong>下载完成后查看脚手架版本</strong><br><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2020/02/12/tvIqEr4Su7Hs8OK.png\" alt=\"react111.PNG\"></p>\n<hr>\n<p><strong>2.创建文件夹 或  用命令创建</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2020/02/12/jFoBXCT9ixAQakE.png\" alt=\"react02.PNG\"></p>\n<hr>\n<p><strong>3.react脚手架搭建项目</strong></p>\n<h5 id=\"reacttext是自己取的项目名称\"><a href=\"#reacttext是自己取的项目名称\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"reacttext是自己取的项目名称\"></a>reacttext是自己取的项目名称</h5><p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2020/02/12/UKp4xzgl7ivJ38T.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<p><strong>搭建成功后出现</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2020/02/12/toT4yDPMk9jRK2d.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<hr>\n<p><strong>4.用编码工具打开终端，我用的是vscode</strong></p>\n<h6 id=\"打开对应文件的终端\"><a href=\"#打开对应文件的终端\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"打开对应文件的终端\"></a>打开对应文件的终端</h6><p>输入：<code>npm